<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" size="6" color="#000066">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" size="4" color="#ff6600"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="6" color="#c0c0c0"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Dear Parents,</span></div><span lang="en-GB"><div style="margin: 0px;"><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">We are pleased to announce that BISM will finally have a new campus in 2017-18 at Los Arqueros. After many twists and turns, the school has finally managed to secure a site with excellent facilities all the way up to Year 13. The facilities will include a large indoor gym, a 25 meter indoor pool and a theatre together with outdoor sports facilities.</font></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">As the new site is 15 minutes from our current campus, we will providing a bus service for the convenience of parents.</font></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">The site is partially built and completion works will begin in the new year.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">We are keen to provide you with more information and answer any questions you might have so we will be holding a presentation event after the Christmas holiday on Saturday, 28th January at 11am at Los Arqueros Golf Club.</font></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">I would like take this opportunity to wish you all a Merry Christmas and Happy New Year.</font></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">With best wishes,</font></div><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif" color="#000000" size="3" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>The British International School of Marbella</font></div></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; "><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font><font class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;" face="Arial, san